Package io.mosip.registration.service.packet.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PacketCreationServiceImpl
    Implementation class of PacketCreationService for creating the Resident Registration as zip file
    PacketEncryptionServiceImpl
    This class encrypts the Registration packet using RSA and AES algorithms.
    PacketExportServiceImpl
    Implementation class for PacketExportService
    PacketHandlerServiceImpl
    The implementation class of PacketHandlerService to handle the registration data to create packet out of it and save the encrypted packet data in the configured local system
    PacketSynchServiceImpl
    This class invokes the external MOSIP service 'Packet Sync' to sync the packet ids, which are ready for upload to the server from client.
    PacketUploadServiceImpl
    This class will update the packet status in the table and also push the packets to the server.
    RegistrationApprovalServiceImpl
    RegistrationApprovalServiceImpl is the registration approval service class
    RegistrationPacketVirusScanServiceImpl
    Implementation class for RegistrationPacketVirusScanService
    RegPacketStatusServiceImpl
    This class will update the packet status in the table after sync with the server.
    ReRegistrationServiceImpl
    Implementation class for ReRegistrationService
